  "title": "一ノ瀬怜1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "（せっかく学校に来たのに、友達がみんな休みだなんて）\n（お昼も一人かぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I came to school after a long absence‚ but all my friends have day off）\n（Alone at lunch‚ too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ、せっかくだし）\n（食レポの練習をしながら食べてみようかしら）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Right‚ since it's been a while）\n（Maybe I'll try eating it while practicing a food report）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9666673024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "（はーい！　現場の一ノ瀬怜です！　私がいただくのは）\n（こちら！　遙子さん手作りのお弁当です）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hiー! Ichinose Rei is here! This is what I am receiving‚）\n（Here it is! Haruko-san's handmade lunch box）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9666673024,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12233.3326976
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "（では早速、開けてみましょう）\n（お弁当箱の一段目には～）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Then‚ let's open it now）\n（On the first layer of lunchbox~）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9333349864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2666683197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "（なんと、ご飯のかわりに）\n（色とりどりのグミが入っていました！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Unexpectedly‚ instead of meal‚）\n（there were colorful gummies inside!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2666683197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.1333347321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "（ん～、お昼にグミを食べることになるなんて驚きです）\n（口の中が甘ったるく……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Umm‚ I'm surprised I'm eating gummy for lunch）\n（My mouth feels sweetish…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3333347321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "――って、なんでグミが入ってるのよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――No‚ why are there gummies in it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3333347321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
