    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "（あら、よく見たら手紙が入ってる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh‚ looking closely‚ there's a letter inside…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6333273569,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4533.334096200001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "（「今日は早朝からお仕事だから、お弁当は他の子達に）\n（任せることにしました。美味しく食べてね。はるこ」）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（'I have work early in the morning today‚ so I decided to leave ）\n（lunch box to other kids. Enjoy your lunch. Haruko'）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1666614531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2333265939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "（他の子達って、明らかに一人は瑠依よね）\n（私のために用意してくれたんだろうけど……はぁ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Other kids‚ one of them is definitely Rui）\n（She prepared it for me‚ but… haa.…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2333265939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "（テレビだったら、すでに放送事故だけど……）\n（き、気を取り直して、食レポしましょう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If it was TV‚ it would already be a broadcasting accident…）\n（C-Calm down and let's do a food report）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5666578927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6333240507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "（あら……？　みなさん、見て下さい！）\n（二段目には、とんかつが入っていました）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh…? Everyone‚ take a look!）\n（Second layer‚ contained pork cutlet）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6333240507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6333235421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "（どうやら、お弁当箱の一段目は瑠依が）\n（二段目はさくらが担当したようですね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It seems like the first layer of lunchbox was taken by Rui）\n（and the second layer by Sakura）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6333235421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9333250679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "（あ～む……。ん～！　冷たくてカッチカチ！）\n（冷凍食品のとんかつを、解凍し忘れて入れたようです）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Yum~m…. Umm~! It's cold and hard!）\n（It seems‚ she forgot to thaw the frozen pork cutlet）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9333250679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3999881741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "（でも大丈夫！　とんかつは冷たくても）\n（さくらの熱い想いは伝わってきました！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ it's okay! Even though the pork cutlet was cold‚）\n（Sakura's passion was conveyed!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3999881741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon",
